    "MissionGiver": "Headhunters",
    "Title": "Hunt Some Heads",
    "Description": "Got some asshole\u2019s trying to push us out of the system. You up for pushing back?\n\nSee, there are some folks who really don\u2019t want us here, and have started sending out hunting parties of five to seven ships, often with a bigger gun ship, to places where we\u2019re building up our presence. Time for us to show that we\u2019re here to stay.  \n\nI\u2019ve strung together a few spots starting at the <EM4>location marker</EM4> on your HUD where we\u2019re seeing the most hostile encounters. Need you to visit each one and scan to see if we can bait them into a fight.\n\nKnow this is going to be a hard one, so don't be cocky and try to go it alone. If I were you, I'd bring at least <EM4>three friends</EM4> onboard for support. To make it worth your while, I'm promising a bonus of <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4> to the main contractor that pulls it off. \n\n- Stows",
